Rating: 4
Hands down the best brownies I've ever had. Everyone loved them, even my husband who prefers a cakey texture (these are fudgy) and I've had several requests for the recipe. One thing to beware of, though it doesn't affect the taste - I used a Ghirardelli white chocolate bar and the result was more yellowish in color and soft, like icing rather than ganache. Make sure you keep them refrigerated or it gets runny.

