Rating: 3
I enjoyed this recipe very much and it was a hit. It's really important that you closely read the instructions to this recipe. It states "Bake brownies until puffed and dry-looking and tester inserted into center comes out with some moist batter attached, about 35 minutes;" If you do that,you'll have delicious brownies with no baking issues whatsoever.

