I thought these were so good because the coffee was just the right amount with the white chocolate ganache. I almost did not put the cinnamon on bc I am not a fan of coffee and cinnamon but it was delicious! My ganache did not firm up like my regular chocolate ganache. They were gone very fast and people wanted the recipe.

Rating: 4
Moist, rich chocolate flavor with just a hint of coffee. Not over- powering so everyone loved them; even my 13 year old. The blend of flavors was delicious right down to the cinnamon. Great with coffee! The recipe is on the small side but they are so rich it was fine for a family of 5. Any more than that and you might want to double it.